{"tid":555632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★收禮金後拒婚　原告指女方結識數月即要錢要樓","createTime":"2018-02-09T15:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T10:22:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"383033190bf722fdaf90572bc50597355dc1b8ef","tid":555632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"年約50至60歲，任職分析師的男原告徐志明指稱，和現年41歲的女被告彭秀玲相識後，曾協議結婚。惟兩人最終未有結婚，原告入稟循民事途徑，追討已支付被告的12萬港元禮金。案件今日(9日)下午在區域法院續審，原告被盤問時透露，透過朋友結識被告，兩人迅即拍拖。被告結識原告不足3個月，便提出要求原告<span style=\"color: red;\">在深圳買樓給她</span>，和贈予20萬港元。原告覺得其要求過份，但回覆對方會考慮。<br />\n<br />\n被告於12年3月遷出原告住所，兩人一度沒有聯絡。至同年6月被告致電原告，稱有宮外孕，在深圳的醫院留醫。原告照顧被告一個多月時間，每星期一至五在港煮飯，然後送到醫院，原告亦替對方支付部份醫藥費。<br />\n<br />\n被告的大律師代表指，被告遷出原告的住所後，兩人仍有親密關係。被告的宮外孕和原告有關，同時被告在事件中把僅餘的輸卵管切除。原告否認與被告的宮外孕有關，並指「可以話係佢既罪孽，媾咁多仔」。原告又引述醫生指，「被告好似落過好多仔」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180209/bkn-20180209171035698-0209_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180209%2Fbkn-20180209171035698-0209_00822_001.html&d=0FMfoBzEZpHi%2FokjrcOfkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=74468b07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180209/bkn-20180209171035698-0209_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c5c13fc146ee3da35f72787ec3f0979a808b39a7","tid":555632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcd0334eb3f36d7095f80b94b43ccf08eb40bd0","tid":555632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5c13fc146ee3da35f72787ec3f0979a808b39a7","tid":555632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:46:35.000Z","msg":"「被告好似落過好多仔」。<br />\n「被告好似落過好多仔」。"},{"pid":"045839f88efd5315af76d63df43b4ee2ac0a2bc4","tid":555632,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"生炒骨(廢老版)"},{"pid":"4b8f0dfc8f38fa0f86b9f1644f09fbb28ca98571","tid":555632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88eab1e7686b9cd849f2c771cf1bc77e922a121a","tid":555632,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"老貓=<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d640c44ba3d0746ccd85fd66a9e4a5d247808d","tid":555632,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebcd1d283617f0de283bbc9f905b44954a829a6","tid":555632,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88eab1e7686b9cd849f2c771cf1bc77e922a121a","tid":555632,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"老貓=<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"老貓係事主"},{"pid":"e1cc2bb11d6572eb688248797844aac7d052c679","tid":555632,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ebcd1d283617f0de283bbc9f905b44954a829a6","tid":555632,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88eab1e7686b9cd849f2c771cf1bc77e922a121a","tid":555632,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"老貓=<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"老貓係事主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c9a831d0ce5b14d68bc3c94